lockWp 
Game: ARMA 2  (1.00) 
Description: Disables switching to the next waypoint (the current waypoint will 
 never complete while lockWp is used). This is sometimes used during 
 cut-scenes.   
Syntax:  
groupName lockWp lockWP 
Parameters: 
groupName: Object or Group 
lockWP: Boolean 
Return Value: 
 Nothing